Function Reference/wp setcookie « WordPress Codex
-----------

This function can be replaced via
[plugins](/Glossary#plugins "Glossary"). If plugins do not redefine
these functions, then this will be used instead.

Sets a cookie for a user who just logged in.

**This function is deprecated. Use
[`wp_set_auth_cookie()`](/Function_Reference/wp_set_auth_cookie "Function Reference/wp set auth cookie")
instead.**

Usage
-----

` <?php wp_setcookie( $username, $password, $already_md5, $home, $siteurl, $remember ) ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$username` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) The user's username
    Default: *None*

 `$password` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) The user's password
    Default: ''

 `$already_md5` 
:   ([*boolean*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Boolean "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Whether the password has already been through MD5
    Default: false

 `$home` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Will be used instead of COOKIEPATH if set
    Default: ''

 `$siteurl` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Will be used instead of SITECOOKIEPATH if set
    Default: ''

 `$remember` 
:   ([*boolean*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Boolean "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Remember that the user is logged in
    Default: false

Return Values
-------------

 void 
:   This function doesn't return anything.

Examples
--------

Notes
-----

-   This function can be replaced via
    [plugins](/Glossary#plugins "Glossary"). If plugins do not redefine
    these functions, then this will be used instead.
-   **This function is deprecated. Use
    [`wp_set_auth_cookie()`](/Function_Reference/wp_set_auth_cookie "Function Reference/wp set auth cookie")
    instead.**

Change Log
----------

-   Since: 1.5
-   Deprecated: 2.5.0

Source File
-----------

`wp_setcookie()` is located in `wp-includes/pluggable.php`.

